data.description: Located within the sought after Timbercrest Subdivision, and just minutes from the heart of the Bearden shopping/business district and I40, sits this well-maintained home on a large 0.4 +/- acre lot. The spacious main level has gleaming hardwood floors, a vaulted-ceiling great room with fireplace, 4 bedrooms/2 baths, and access to the oversized screened porch. Downstairs is a spacious rec-room with new LVP flooring, the 2nd fireplace, wet bar, and patio doors that lead out to a large patio. Bedroom number 5 is also located downstairs, as well as a 1/2 bath and laundry room.  The 2 car garage is large, and approximately 28' by 24'.  A community pool is available, for an annual fee.
